{
  "video_id": "jMBdQW2LLxw",
  "title": "Derek Paravicini and Adam Ockelford: In the key of genius",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12491.0,
      "end_time": 13836.0,
      "text": "Adam Ockelford: I promise there won&#39;t be too much"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13836.0,
      "end_time": 16248.0,
      "text": "of me talking, and a lot of Derek playing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16248.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18692.0,
      "text": "but I thought it would just be nice to recap"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18692.0,
      "end_time": 22628.0,
      "text": "on how Derek got to where he is today."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22628.0,
      "end_time": 25119.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s amazing now, because he&#39;s so much bigger than me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25119.0,
      "end_time": 26737.0,
      "text": "but when Derek was born,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26737.0,
      "end_time": 29375.0,
      "text": "he could have fitted on the palm of your hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29376.0,
      "end_time": 32340.0,
      "text": "He was born three and a half months premature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32340.000000000004,
      "end_time": 37556.0,
      "text": "and really it was a fantastic fight for him to survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37556.0,
      "end_time": 38775.0,
      "text": "He had to have a lot of oxygen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38776.0,
      "end_time": 40776.0,
      "text": "and that affected your eyes, Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40776.0,
      "end_time": 42604.0,
      "text": "and also the way you understand language"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42604.0,
      "end_time": 45575.0,
      "text": "and the way you understand the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45575.0,
      "end_time": 47642.0,
      "text": "But that was the end of the bad news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47657.0,
      "end_time": 50647.0,
      "text": "because when Derek came home from the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50648.0,
      "end_time": 53830.0,
      "text": "his family decided to employ the redoubtable nanny"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53830.0,
      "end_time": 56201.0,
      "text": "who was going to look after you, Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56201.0,
      "end_time": 58849.0,
      "text": "really for the rest of your childhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58849.0,
      "end_time": 61425.0,
      "text": "And Nanny&#39;s great insight, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61425.0,
      "end_time": 64110.0,
      "text": "was to think, here&#39;s a child who can&#39;t see."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64110.0,
      "end_time": 67310.0,
      "text": "Music must be the thing for Derek."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67310.0,
      "end_time": 71298.0,
      "text": "And sure enough, she sang, or as Derek called it, warbled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71298.0,
      "end_time": 74843.0,
      "text": "to him for his first few years of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74843.0,
      "end_time": 78894.0,
      "text": "And I think it was that excitement with hearing her voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78894.0,
      "end_time": 81878.0,
      "text": "hour after hour every day that made him think"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81878.0,
      "end_time": 84896.0,
      "text": "maybe, you know, in his brain something was stirring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84896.0,
      "end_time": 87905.0,
      "text": "some sort of musical gift."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87905.0,
      "end_time": 90178.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a little picture of Derek going up now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90178.0,
      "end_time": 93852.0,
      "text": "when you were with your nanny."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93852.0,
      "end_time": 97371.0,
      "text": "Now Nanny&#39;s great other insight was to think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97371.0,
      "end_time": 100705.0,
      "text": "perhaps we should get Derek something to play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100706.0,
      "end_time": 104342.0,
      "text": "and sure enough, she dragged this little keyboard"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104342.0,
      "end_time": 106923.0,
      "text": "out of the loft, never thinking really"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106938.0,
      "end_time": 109281.0,
      "text": "that anything much would come of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109281.0,
      "end_time": 112269.0,
      "text": "But Derek, your tiny hand must have gone out to that thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112269.0,
      "end_time": 113890.0,
      "text": "and actually bashed it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113890.0,
      "end_time": 116679.0,
      "text": "bashed it so hard they thought it was going to break."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116679.0,
      "end_time": 120671.0,
      "text": "But out of all the bashing, after a few months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120671.0,
      "end_time": 123840.0,
      "text": "emerged the most fantastic music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123840.0,
      "end_time": 127206.0,
      "text": "and I think there was just a miracle moment, really, Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127206.0,
      "end_time": 131721.0,
      "text": "when you realized that all the sounds you hear in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131721.0,
      "end_time": 135321.0,
      "text": "out there is something that you can copy on the keyboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 135321.0,
      "end_time": 137834.0,
      "text": "That was the great eureka moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137834.0,
      "end_time": 140404.0,
      "text": "Now, not being able to see meant, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 140404.0,
      "end_time": 141595.0,
      "text": "that you taught yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141595.0,
      "end_time": 142919.0,
      "text": "Derek Paravicini: I taught myself to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142919.0,
      "end_time": 144216.0,
      "text": "AO: You did teach yourself to play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 144216.0,
      "end_time": 146747.0,
      "text": "and as a consequence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 146747.0,
      "end_time": 147798.0,
      "text": "playing the piano for you, Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147798.0,
      "end_time": 150275.0,
      "text": "was a lot of knuckles and karate chops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150275.0,
      "end_time": 152731.0,
      "text": "and even a bit of nose going on in there."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152731.0,
      "end_time": 156590.0,
      "text": "And now, here&#39;s what Nanny did also do"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156590.0,
      "end_time": 159381.0,
      "text": "was to press the record button on one of those little"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 159381.0,
      "end_time": 161939.0,
      "text": "early tape recorders that they had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161939.0,
      "end_time": 164420.0,
      "text": "and this is a wonderful tape, now, of Derek playing"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164420.0,
      "end_time": 165454.0,
      "text": "when you were four years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 165454.0,
      "end_time": 168152.0,
      "text": "DP: \"Molly Malone (Cockles and Mussels).\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168152.0,
      "end_time": 169214.0,
      "text": "AO: It wasn&#39;t actually \"Cockles and Mussels.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169214.0,
      "end_time": 171364.0,
      "text": "This one is \"English Country Garden.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 171364.0,
      "end_time": 173629.0,
      "text": "DP: \"English Country Garden.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 173629.0,
      "end_time": 181887.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"English Country Garden\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210521.0,
      "end_time": 212319.0,
      "text": "AO: There you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212319.0,
      "end_time": 219476.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 219477.0,
      "end_time": 221383.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s just fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 221383.0,
      "end_time": 223113.0,
      "text": "You know, there&#39;s this little child who can&#39;t see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223113.0,
      "end_time": 225320.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t really understand much about the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 225320.0,
      "end_time": 228250.0,
      "text": "has no one in the family who plays an instrument,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228260.0,
      "end_time": 230327.0,
      "text": "and yet he taught himself to play that."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 230327.0,
      "end_time": 231559.0,
      "text": "And as you can see from the picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 231559.0,
      "end_time": 233918.0,
      "text": "there was quite a lot of body action going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 233918.0,
      "end_time": 235719.0,
      "text": "while you were playing, Derek."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235719.0,
      "end_time": 240289.0,
      "text": "Now, along -- Derek and I met when he was four and a half years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240289.0,
      "end_time": 244107.0,
      "text": "and at first, Derek, I thought you were mad, to be honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 244107.0,
      "end_time": 245921.0,
      "text": "because when you played the piano,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245921.0,
      "end_time": 248838.0,
      "text": "you seemed to want to play every single note on the keyboard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248838.0,
      "end_time": 250245.0,
      "text": "and also you had this little habit"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250246.0,
      "end_time": 252429.0,
      "text": "of hitting me out of the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252429.0,
      "end_time": 254235.0,
      "text": "So as soon as I tried to get near the piano,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 254235.0,
      "end_time": 256383.0,
      "text": "I was firmly shoved off."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 256382.0,
      "end_time": 259670.0,
      "text": "And having said to your dad, Nic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259670.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261562.00000000003,
      "text": "that I would try to teach you, I was then slightly confused"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 261562.0,
      "end_time": 263149.0,
      "text": "as to how I might go about that"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 263149.0,
      "end_time": 265550.0,
      "text": "if I wasn&#39;t allowed near the piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 265550.0,
      "end_time": 267727.0,
      "text": "But after a while, I thought, well, the only way"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 267727.0,
      "end_time": 271828.0,
      "text": "is to just pick you up, shove Derek over to the other side of the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 271828.0,
      "end_time": 274972.0,
      "text": "and in the 10 seconds that I got before Derek came back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 274972.0,
      "end_time": 277149.0,
      "text": "I could just play something very quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 277149.0,
      "end_time": 279141.0,
      "text": "for him to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 279141.0,
      "end_time": 280543.0,
      "text": "And in the end, Derek, I think you agreed"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 280543.0,
      "end_time": 284523.0,
      "text": "that we could actually have some fun playing the piano together."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 284523.0,
      "end_time": 287348.0,
      "text": "As you can see, there&#39;s me in my early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 287348.0,
      "end_time": 289587.0,
      "text": "pre-marriage days with a brown beard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 289587.0,
      "end_time": 293233.0,
      "text": "and little Derek concentrating there."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293233.0,
      "end_time": 295777.0,
      "text": "I just realized this is going to be recorded, isn&#39;t it? Right. Okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 295777.0,
      "end_time": 297790.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 297790.0,
      "end_time": 301300.0,
      "text": "Now then, by the age of 10, Derek really"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 301300.0,
      "end_time": 303352.0,
      "text": "had taken the world by storm."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 303352.0,
      "end_time": 306369.0,
      "text": "This is a photo of you, Derek, playing at the Barbican"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 306370.0,
      "end_time": 308810.0,
      "text": "with the Royal Philharmonic Pops."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 308810.0,
      "end_time": 312650.0,
      "text": "Basically it was just an exciting journey, really."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 312650.0,
      "end_time": 314791.0,
      "text": "And in those days, Derek, you didn&#39;t speak very much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 314791.0,
      "end_time": 317102.0,
      "text": "and so there was always a moment of tension"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 317102.0,
      "end_time": 320630.0,
      "text": "as to whether you&#39;d actually understood what it was we were going to play"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 320630.0,
      "end_time": 322574.0,
      "text": "and whether you&#39;d play the right piece in the right key,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 322574.0,
      "end_time": 324330.0,
      "text": "and all that kind of thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 324330.0,
      "end_time": 326858.0,
      "text": "But the orchestra were wowed as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 326858.0,
      "end_time": 330715.0,
      "text": "and the press of the world were fascinated by your ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 330715.0,
      "end_time": 334510.0,
      "text": "to play these fantastic pieces."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 334520.0,
      "end_time": 337114.0,
      "text": "Now the question is, how do you do it, Derek?"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 337114.0,
      "end_time": 339685.0,
      "text": "And hopefully we can show the audience now"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 339685.0,
      "end_time": 342737.0,
      "text": "how it is you do what you do."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 342737.0,
      "end_time": 344570.0,
      "text": "I think that one of the first things that happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 344570.0,
      "end_time": 345847.0,
      "text": "when you were very little, Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 345847.0,
      "end_time": 348183.0,
      "text": "was that by the time you were two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 348183.0,
      "end_time": 353162.0,
      "text": "your musical ear had already outstripped that of most adults."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 353162.0,
      "end_time": 355960.0,
      "text": "And so whenever you heard any note at all --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 355960.0,
      "end_time": 357864.0,
      "text": "if I just play a random note --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 357864.0,
      "end_time": 360277.0,
      "text": "(Piano notes) --"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 360292.0,
      "end_time": 362183.0,
      "text": "you knew instantly what it was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 362183.0,
      "end_time": 366421.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;d got the ability as well to find that note on the piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 366421.0,
      "end_time": 368900.0,
      "text": "Now that&#39;s called perfect pitch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 368900.0,
      "end_time": 371246.0,
      "text": "and some people have perfect pitch for a few white notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 371246.0,
      "end_time": 372395.0,
      "text": "in the middle of the piano."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 372396.0,
      "end_time": 378424.0,
      "text": "(Piano notes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 378424.0,
      "end_time": 381849.0,
      "text": "You can see how -- you get a sense of playing with Derek."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 381850.0,
      "end_time": 385398.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 385398.0,
      "end_time": 388424.0,
      "text": "But Derek, your ear is so much more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 388424.0,
      "end_time": 389851.0,
      "text": "If I just put the microphone down for a bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 389851.0,
      "end_time": 392571.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to play a cluster of notes."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 392571.0,
      "end_time": 394887.0,
      "text": "Those of you who can see will know how many notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 394887.0,
      "end_time": 395896.0,
      "text": "but Derek, of course, can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 395896.0,
      "end_time": 398798.0,
      "text": "Not only can you say how many notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 398798.0,
      "end_time": 404222.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s being able to play them all at the same time. Here we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 404222.0,
      "end_time": 411299.0,
      "text": "(Chords)"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 414103.0,
      "end_time": 416921.0,
      "text": "Well, forget the terminology, Derek. Fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 416921.0,
      "end_time": 421866.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s that ability, that ability to hear simultaneous sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 421866.0,
      "end_time": 424188.0,
      "text": "not only just single sounds, but when a whole orchestra is playing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 424188.0,
      "end_time": 426960.0,
      "text": "Derek, you can hear every note,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 426960.0,
      "end_time": 429352.0,
      "text": "and instantly, through all those hours and hours of practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 429352.0,
      "end_time": 431310.0,
      "text": "reproduce those on the keyboard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 431310.0,
      "end_time": 435577.0,
      "text": "that makes you, I think, is the basis of all your ability."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 435577.0,
      "end_time": 438180.0,
      "text": "Now then."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 438180.0,
      "end_time": 441748.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s no use having that kind of raw ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 441748.0,
      "end_time": 443509.0,
      "text": "without the technique,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 443509.0,
      "end_time": 445431.0,
      "text": "and luckily, Derek, you decided that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 445431.0,
      "end_time": 448530.0,
      "text": "once we did start learning, you&#39;d let me help you"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 448530.0,
      "end_time": 449692.0,
      "text": "learn all the scale fingerings."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 449692.0,
      "end_time": 452639.0,
      "text": "So for example using your thumb under with C major."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 452639.0,
      "end_time": 457752.0,
      "text": "(Piano notes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 457752.0,
      "end_time": 461766.0,
      "text": "Etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 464161.0,
      "end_time": 467521.0,
      "text": "And in the end, you got so quick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 467521.0,
      "end_time": 469395.0,
      "text": "that things like \"Flight of the Bumblebee\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 469395.0,
      "end_time": 470625.0,
      "text": "were no problem, were they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 470625.0,
      "end_time": 471903.0,
      "text": "DP: No."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 471903.0,
      "end_time": 474532.0,
      "text": "AO: Right. So here, by the age of 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 474532.0,
      "end_time": 476503.0,
      "text": "Derek was playing things like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 476504.0,
      "end_time": 479586.0,
      "text": "DP: This."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 479586.0,
      "end_time": 493259.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 547792.0,
      "end_time": 549358.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 549358.0,
      "end_time": 551834.0,
      "text": "AO: Derek, let&#39;s have a bow."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 563408.0,
      "end_time": 567480.0,
      "text": "Well done."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 567480.0,
      "end_time": 571403.0,
      "text": "Now the truly amazing thing was, with all those scales, Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 571403.0,
      "end_time": 573638.0,
      "text": "you could not only play \"Flight of the Bumblebee\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 573638.0,
      "end_time": 576304.0,
      "text": "in the usual key, but any note I play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 576304.0,
      "end_time": 578297.0,
      "text": "Derek can play it on."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 578297.0,
      "end_time": 580765.0,
      "text": "So if I just choose a note at random, like that one."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 580765.0,
      "end_time": 582580.0,
      "text": "(Piano notes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 582580.0,
      "end_time": 584184.0,
      "text": "Can you play \"Flight of the Bumblebee\" on that note?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 584184.0,
      "end_time": 586488.0,
      "text": "DP: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\" on that note."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 586488.0,
      "end_time": 590853.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 592178.0,
      "end_time": 596251.0,
      "text": "AO: Or another one? How about in G minor?"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 596251.0,
      "end_time": 598521.0,
      "text": "DP: G minor."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 598522.0,
      "end_time": 603833.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"Flight of the Bumblebee\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 603833.0,
      "end_time": 606117.0,
      "text": "AO: Fantastic. Well done, Derek."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 606117.0,
      "end_time": 609899.0,
      "text": "So you see, in your brain, Derek, is this amazing musical computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 609899.0,
      "end_time": 613598.0,
      "text": "that can instantly recalibrate, recalculate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 613598.0,
      "end_time": 615770.0,
      "text": "all the pieces in the world that are out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 615770.0,
      "end_time": 618197.0,
      "text": "Most pianists would have a heart attack if you said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 618197.0,
      "end_time": 620140.0,
      "text": "\"Sorry, do you mind playing &#39;Flight of the Bumblebee&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 620140.0,
      "end_time": 623244.0,
      "text": "in B minor instead of A minor?\" as we went on."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 623244.0,
      "end_time": 626665.0,
      "text": "In fact, the first time, Derek, you played that with an orchestra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 626665.0,
      "end_time": 628754.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d learned the version that you&#39;d learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 628754.0,
      "end_time": 630983.0,
      "text": "and then the orchestra, in fact, did have a different version,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 630983.0,
      "end_time": 633460.0,
      "text": "so while we were waiting in the two hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 633461.0,
      "end_time": 635463.0,
      "text": "before the rehearsal and the concert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 635463.0,
      "end_time": 637703.0,
      "text": "Derek listened to the different version and learned it quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 637703.0,
      "end_time": 640180.0,
      "text": "and then was able to play it with the orchestra."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 640180.0,
      "end_time": 641640.0,
      "text": "Fantastic chap."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 641640.0,
      "end_time": 645980.0,
      "text": "The other wonderful thing about you is memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 645990.0,
      "end_time": 648935.0,
      "text": "DP: Memory. AO: Your memory is truly amazing, and every concert we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 648935.0,
      "end_time": 651765.0,
      "text": "we ask the audience to participate, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 651765.0,
      "end_time": 655529.0,
      "text": "by suggesting a piece Derek might like to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 655529.0,
      "end_time": 657510.0,
      "text": "And people say, \"Well, that&#39;s terribly brave"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 657510.0,
      "end_time": 659276.0,
      "text": "because what happens if Derek doesn&#39;t know it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 659276.0,
      "end_time": 660287.0,
      "text": "And I say, \"No, it&#39;s not brave at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 660288.0,
      "end_time": 662940.0,
      "text": "because if you ask for something that Derek doesn&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 662940.0,
      "end_time": 664541.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re invited to come and sing it first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 664541.0,
      "end_time": 667270.0,
      "text": "and then he&#39;ll pick it up.\" (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 667270.0,
      "end_time": 671742.0,
      "text": "So just be thoughtful before you suggest something too outlandish."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 671742.0,
      "end_time": 675459.0,
      "text": "But seriously, would anyone like to choose a piece?"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 675459.0,
      "end_time": 679391.0,
      "text": "DP: Choose a piece. Choose, choose, would you like to choose? AO: Because it&#39;s quite dark. You&#39;ll just have to shout out."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 679392.0,
      "end_time": 682213.0,
      "text": "Would you like to hear me play?"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 682213.0,
      "end_time": 683427.0,
      "text": "(Audience: \"Theme of Paganini.\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 683427.0,
      "end_time": 686389.0,
      "text": "AO: Paganini. DP: \"The Theme of Paganini.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 686389.0,
      "end_time": 688227.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 688227.0,
      "end_time": 710137.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"Theme of Paganini\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 783178.0,
      "end_time": 794409.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 794409.0,
      "end_time": 800223.0,
      "text": "AO: Well done."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 800223.0,
      "end_time": 802896.0,
      "text": "Derek&#39;s going to L.A. soon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 802897.0,
      "end_time": 806119.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a milestone, because it means that Derek and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 806119.0,
      "end_time": 809490.0,
      "text": "will have spent over 100 hours on long-haul flights together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 809490.0,
      "end_time": 812117.0,
      "text": "which is quite interesting, isn&#39;t it Derek?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 812117.0,
      "end_time": 815468.0,
      "text": "DP: Very interesting, Adam, yes. Long-haul flights. Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 815468.0,
      "end_time": 817930.0,
      "text": "AO: You may think 13 hours is a long time to keep talking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 817930.0,
      "end_time": 820448.0,
      "text": "but Derek does it effortlessly. Now then."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 820448.0,
      "end_time": 822560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 822560.0,
      "end_time": 824434.0,
      "text": "But in America, they&#39;ve coined this term,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 824434.0,
      "end_time": 826440.0,
      "text": "\"the human iPod\" for Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 826440.0,
      "end_time": 828400.0,
      "text": "which I think is just missing the point, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 828400.0,
      "end_time": 831477.0,
      "text": "because Derek, you&#39;re so much more than an iPod."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 831477.0,
      "end_time": 834264.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re a fantastic, creative musician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 834264.0,
      "end_time": 837215.0,
      "text": "and I think that was nowhere clearer to see, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 837215.0,
      "end_time": 839412.0,
      "text": "than when we went to Slovenia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 839412.0,
      "end_time": 844809.0,
      "text": "and someone -- in a longer concert we tend to get people joining in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 844809.0,
      "end_time": 848463.0,
      "text": "and this person, very, very nervously came onto the stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 848463.0,
      "end_time": 850997.0,
      "text": "DP: He played \"Chopsticks.\" AO: And played \"Chopsticks.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 850998.0,
      "end_time": 852489.0,
      "text": "DP: \"Chopsticks.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 852489.0,
      "end_time": 855853.0,
      "text": "AO: A bit like this. DP: Like this. Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 855853.0,
      "end_time": 856790.0,
      "text": "(Piano notes)"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 856791.0,
      "end_time": 858471.0,
      "text": "AO: I should really get Derek&#39;s manager to come and play it."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 858471.0,
      "end_time": 859695.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s sitting there."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 859695.0,
      "end_time": 862973.0,
      "text": "DP: Somebody played \"Chopsticks\" like this. AO: Just teasing, right? Here we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 862973.0,
      "end_time": 864228.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"Chopsticks\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 864229.0,
      "end_time": 866491.0,
      "text": "DP: Let Derek play it."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 866491.0,
      "end_time": 868640.0,
      "text": "AO: What did you do with it, Derek?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 868640.0,
      "end_time": 869805.0,
      "text": "DP: I got to improvise with it, Adam."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 869805.0,
      "end_time": 873372.0,
      "text": "AO: This is Derek the musician."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 873372.0,
      "end_time": 881483.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"Chopsticks\" improvisation)"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 929783.0,
      "end_time": 931860.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 931860.0,
      "end_time": 935636.0,
      "text": "(Music) (Clapping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 935636.0,
      "end_time": 937776.0,
      "text": "Keep up with Derek."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 937777.0,
      "end_time": 945274.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 992170.0,
      "end_time": 998589.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 1015130.0,
      "end_time": 1016578.0,
      "text": "The TED people will kill me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 1016580.0,
      "end_time": 1018636.0,
      "text": "but perhaps there&#39;s time for one encore."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 1018640.0,
      "end_time": 1022465.0,
      "text": "DP: For one encore. AO: One encore, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 1022460.0,
      "end_time": 1024515.0,
      "text": "So this is one of Derek&#39;s heroes."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 1024520.0,
      "end_time": 1026692.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the great Art Tatum -- DP: Art Tatum."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 1026690.0,
      "end_time": 1028717.0,
      "text": "AO: -- who also was a pianist who couldn&#39;t see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 1028710.0,
      "end_time": 1029866.0,
      "text": "and also, I think, like Derek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 1029869.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1031378.9999999999,
      "text": "thought that all the world was a piano,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 1031380.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1033341.0000000001,
      "text": "so whenever Art Tatum plays something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 1033339.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1035973.9999999999,
      "text": "it sounds like there&#39;s three pianos in the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 1035970.0,
      "end_time": 1041795.0,
      "text": "And here is Derek&#39;s take on Art Tatum&#39;s take on \"Tiger Rag.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 1041800.0,
      "end_time": 1045536.0,
      "text": "DP: \"Tiger Rag.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 1045530.0,
      "end_time": 1064698.0,
      "text": "(Music: \"Tiger Rag\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 1155870.0,
      "end_time": 1159870.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}